 for their half finished games essentially outsourcing some of their best content to third parties who have none of the benefits of being full time bethesda employees additionally the feedback for the paid content is now completely biased as only the users who purchased the mod will be able to write reviews and rate the content if valve and bethesda truly wanted to legitimately support the modding community all they had to do was add an optional donation option for those who want to contribute to the mods development i am not blaming any of the developers of the game they did what they were told their marketting department and those above it are solely the ones blamed as well as the service who hosts their game
