e of one of the greatest aspects of pc gaming take dlc multiply it by hundreds or even thousands remove all quality control add an abundance of intellectual property theft remove all guarantees of functionality and compatibility and on top of that possibly and quite likely remove any chance of a free alternative with the establishment of a monopoly on thirdparty content that is purchaseonly in the future and you will have paidmods if people give even an inkling of interest in this it will spread and we will have to kiss the days of being able to fix and improve our favorite games without simultaneously exploiting our very own friends and colleagues for the benefit of faceless greedy corporations in our actions goodbye
