rts of blowing  up be one sneaky  or just go chop heads off to space then shout at their corpse giggling as you watch it fly ride ing dragons and then if youre still bored mods oh god the mods dont like how the stealth system works just grab a overhaul patch you have more than you think to choose from want to fish havesex have an alternate start say  no to the lockpicking system and get a pro version more books morrrrrrrrrreeee books entire questlines made by fans of skyrim or you can just make it and i still have things to say the story of skyrim has two different main storylines and hundreds of side stories to get involved in people will love you or hate you depending on what you do if youre a thief and a assassin in the respective guildsyou will be very very infamous in fact so much so that if a guard tries to apprehend you you can scare them into not arresting you the civil war crisis and the dragons return crisis you can pick and choose between every quest you can always go back and continue on it later hell you dont even have to do the main questlines ive still yet to get around to even getting them halfway done and the civil war crisis has two sides to pick from once you choose the only way to see the other questline is to replay the game and pick the other side and even if you completely ignore those two storylines you still have hundreds of hours of gametime to go through and the dlc get it get it all they are all worth it i actually have only one minor complaint about skyrim but honestly its actually small for me they could have used more voice actors for each race now that might sound bad for immersion but the actors do so well in voicing their lines its easy to forgive honestly skyrims one of the few games that i truely believe to be perfect that rating for me stands with unthinkable natural law final fantasy crystal chronicles and epic battle fantasy 4 story 1010 this is one game you need to read its lore within the game and pay attention to whats going on around you solid masterpiece music 910 i sometimes forget the music is there but i think thats because they blend too well with the game combat 8510 once i got a few overhaul patches and the dance of death mod its a perfect 1110 content 1010 this is one of those games that even at the average 60$ price tag of aaa games today is still a steal the dlcs just make this already expansive game even bigger overall rating to be fair i think a 9210 will suffice my last words to you by reading this you are now krii lun ausd marked for death es
