 is split between the hobbyists and the ones with dollar signs in their eyes mods are being pirated there are heated debates going on and frontiers are building up between former allies for the coming cold war and inevitable skirmishes nothing of this existed as mods were free its just sad all because of a little money the game itself would get a maybe 6810 btw depending on what youre into this downvote results from the idiots in suits that forgot why there is modding in the first place and thus harming this game as well as modding in general
