hing place a stolen thing change numbers in a book after stealing 20 times in a row the same object you kinda loose it no pun intended  the leveling system is way to prolonged i dont mind spending a lot of hours in a game especially a rpg but come on one has to spent a whole eternity to actually become a badass character in even one skill by the time youre for example a 100 level marskman youve already finished all the fractions youre interested in  the necessity of mods i dont know what stuff the developers smoked during testing but the interface of this game is probably the definitively worst i have ever encountered even after installing the mod skyui its horrible and slow as hell absolutely horrible like i mentioned in the beginning this game is completely overhyped and overrated in every aspect in conclusion this game tries to have and be anything but isnt its like jack of all trades master of none still if you have 15 bucks left buy it
