he general of the stormcloaks or the legate of the empire then if you want to be an archer so be it find yourself a bow and some arrows or you could be a powerful mage or maybe a bit of both the customation is limitless you dont have to just be a fighter you can be a smith or a enchanter then again you could be a alchemist you can have a wife or a husband depending on who you want to be the game never ceases to amaze me the difficulty never changes the creatures will scale to your level then some will just be hard the rest of the game as well as some monsters like wolves are just there to say hi so keep in mind who youre dealing with maybe if you are about to fight something strong do some research this game will show you what its like to be the chosen one to save a planet the dlcs cost much but are certainly worth it one you will learn what it means to be dragonborn by fighting the very first dragonborn another will let you live life with your family in a house and a child then the last one will make you shiver as you fight vampires or become one thanks to this game having a workshop you can even expand the world this game will teach you that life is what you make of it you can either make lemonade with your lemons or throw them back at the world you can break the law at your own will be you will learn there will be a punishment you can help the people of skyrim and feel the greatness of helping someone out the reward will not matter to you just the smile on their face as you give them back their prized whatever it is or you can help people just get some coin in your pocket either way it doesnt matter you can be the best blackmailer or the nicest person alive you can learn the history of skyrim heck you can even learn the history of all of tamriel if you havent and or dont want to play the previous titles no problem they have hidden books all over skyrim that tell you the story of oblivion and earlier titles if you love a game that isnt too much for you to take in and love a customation at the same time being your own person then this game is for you if you love slaying dragons with just three words and terrorising villages you will love this game if you want to save people from the evils of the planet and gain some new friends this will be your standing stone of glory i heavily recommend this game for any of those people out there that want a new adventure that will change your life
